{{flavour|This spell protects the caster from electric shocks.}}

'''Insulation''' is a level 4 [[Charms]]/[[Air Magic]] spell which temporarily grants the caster [[electricity]] resistance. As this resistance is one of the harder ones to come by, it may be worth considering.

==Notes==
The term "insulation" is occasionally used by players as a synonym for electricity resistance from any source, since it is described on artefacts as "It insulates you from electricty".

==History==
Insulation was removed in [[0.12]].

